      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This car is the perfect canvas for your next big project. While it is currently in poor condition and will require mechanical work and some TLC to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic opportunity to rebuild a vehicle exactly how you want it. If you're looking for a rewarding challenge at a great entry price, this is the one for you!",
