    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronics functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid; the engine runs smoothly, the brakes are responsive, and it has a complete service history. This is a reliable, high-quality vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing any immediate repairs.",
